    Fields in Unnamed Package declared as Resource
    Modifier and Type
    Field
    Description
    private Resource
    CardResource.resource
    Indicates the type of resource this card represents.
    It is used by the GUI and CLI to determine the color of the card.
    If the card is played Face-down, the card will give the player 1 unit of the resource stated in the field.
    private Resource
    Corner.resource
    Describes which resource is contained in the corner.
    Fields in Unnamed Package with type parameters of type Resource
    Modifier and Type
    Field
    Description
    private Map<Coordinates,Resource>
    Model.Objectives.ObjectiveGeometric.cardPattern
    Map containing the required pattern to satisfy the objective.
    The Keys of the map are the coordinates of the pattern and the Values are the Resource/Color of the pattern.
    private Map<Resource,Integer>
    CardStarter.centralResources
    Map containing the resources in the center of the card.
    The Keys of the map are the Resources and the Values are number of units for a given resource.
    private Map<Resource,Integer>
    CardGolden.constraint
    Stores information about the playability constraint;
    The key of the map is the resource, and the value is an integer indicating how many units of that resource are required.
    private Map<Resource,Integer>
    Player.playerResourcesCounter
    A map that is functionally a counter for the Resources currently held by the player.
    private Map<Resource,Integer>
    Model.Objectives.ObjectiveResource.requiredResources
    Map containing the required resources to satisfy the objective.
    The Keys of the map are the resources and the Values are the number of units required.
